snippet.textDisplay:
For people who compare pakistani and indian music.. 
They are 2 completely different stuff.
Pakistan has sufi .. India has hindustani classical. 

We are in love with sufi.. Because it has this roohani vibe to it... Which is more relatable.. Easy to grasp and comprehend.

Whereasp hindustani classical is too technical.. Its music at its roots.. 


They way i see it is... 

Sufi is for ALLAH ki IBADAT

And hindustani classical is for SANGEET ki PUJA. 

Ps: dont compare bolly music to coke studio pakistan..  Its an insult to coke studio.
